RELEASE NOTES

Get ready for the largest and most exciting DLC for Euro Truck
Simulator 2 so far. This map expansion features Sweden, Norway and
Denmark, with mile upon mile of scenic roads and numerous landmarks to
see across these three beautiful Nordic countries. New ferry terminals
also allow you to board ferries directly and access the coastal cities
plus use new sea routes to ports in northern Germany, Poland, and the
United Kingdom. Discover 27 Scandinavian cities including Stockholm,
Malm , G teborg, Oslo, Stavanger, Bergen, K benhavn, Aalborg and
Esbjerg...

Features:

Improved daylight cycle and weather visuals
